rComments: What he wants our assignments to be is different from the actual assignment guidelines he gives us. His TAs who grade the paper all want different things (that often directly oppose what he says) make assignments a nightmare. Awad is so personable and relatable. He is a true teacher and is definitely caring and stimulating. He challenges you with your coursework instead of allowing the class to be lazy.

Professor Ibrahim is an AMAZING professor. He really makes an effort to connect with his students on a personal level and it is obvious that he really enjoys being a professor. He is also very patient and takes the time to answer questions well. He is passionate, funny, and he knows what he is talking about. I highly recommend him 100%

Terrible professor. Does not respond to student questions or provide any feedback on assignments. I would NEVER take a course with this professor again.
The worst class i have taken so far.

This was the best class I ever took!! Class discussions were interactive and he is a first class human being!
He is one of the most helpful student while I was student
